  "temporal_coverage": "Historical USGS video cruises represented by Data Series 781",
  "limitations": [
    "Not for navigation.",
    "Cruises were targeted to validate sonar interpretations and are not a uniform seafloor sample.",
    "This source is admitted only for a raw endpoint-support audit; it has no raster-alignment, model-training, validation, scoring, or production authority.",
